  77,36,nor will they be permitted to offer excuses
  77,37,Woe on that Day to the deniers
  77,38,"ЋєThey will be told by Allah,ЋЇ вАЬThis is the Day of ЋєFinalЋЇ Decision: We have gathered you along with earlier disbelievers Ћєfor punishmentЋЇ"
  77,39,"So if you have a scheme Ћєto save yourselvesЋЇ, then use it against Me.вАЭ"
