  78,27,For they never expected any reckoning
  78,28,and totally rejected Our signs
  78,29,And We have everything recorded precisely
  78,30,"ЋєSo the deniers will be told,ЋЇ вАЬTaste Ћєthe punishmentЋЇ, for all you will get from Us is more torment.вАЭ"
  78,31,"Indeed, the righteous will have salvationвАФ"
